{"tid":2492293,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"痴撚線 蜪寶賣貓係咩事？","createTime":"2021-04-17T04:12:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T04:27:58.000Z","uid":236080,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1bc27e5fba934ea846cf4fc18f99d240722f907b","tid":2492293,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T04:12:25.000Z","msg":"今日屋企廢老飲茶個陣上蜪寶<br />\n佢攞俾我睇問我：「呢啲係咪真貓？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：貓？？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPvNsBypDHt7o4gYvhvhAyYpeYs3zcRLJJRRPWncgFwED?filename=orG1fcs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2ForG1fcs.png&h=1e15db50&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVkZvtCJixrZBbU4X7zSY4TYDnniuc2BpaAfoaGA32PJ7?filename=9L8ZMi8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9L8ZMi8.png&h=4f0c191f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmW9rTAcSL29LM8QB86cw7a7DWsHSnkTL3FuuifUPkKLmc?filename=DJSS6i8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDJSS6i8.png&h=9e588d30&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRTcbgQ1BQw1fyBkx1ETtdo14mp1D44MCVzoH2c4a1jQa?filename=DRs7Vcu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDRs7Vcu.png&h=7e319f17&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmafVPSzxWDnqqPJmQPVRYbV9qMHU5VUJypAq8gFaT2Ccc?filename=7WzVjEa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7WzVjEa.png&h=82366fbd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfTSX7r2Mh5RBFC3JsYWmGA9vaCS1u7G52mydxUgC6Qwr?filename=iOVmfcv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiOVmfcv.png&h=0b7bfda3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNQLYMgw5e3V38xeAnf8L5wcsW3CoQz7sriw4nUwVpEWn?filename=DRkpXqR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDRkpXqR.png&h=e41a3972&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1）啲貓未必打齊針<br />\n2）買家未必識養貓<br />\n3）運送過程空運/陸運，會唔會俾人放係箱/行李箱<br />\n4）生命&ne;賣買貨品<br />\n5）一陣俾啲人買翻去當野味味hihi<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌dnlm<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算我下世投胎唔做人，去做貓，都要做英國貓美國貓啊hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好撚癲啊屌你支蟈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31dbd28d12bf5a1659bb59957009d3fe45dff270","tid":2492293,"uid":49151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T04:13:17.000Z","msg":"擺明係賣嚟食"},{"pid":"0ee9dce032dd0245ae85414e9590d7e29f4ba07e","tid":2492293,"uid":24282,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T04:14:12.000Z","msg":"買賣植物就得<br />\n動物就唔得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"febede2064deab014e7dd2bae2ecb3c849ad6f00","tid":2492293,"uid":236080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"31dbd28d12bf5a1659bb59957009d3fe45dff270","tid":2492293,"uid":49151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T04:13:17.000Z","msg":"擺明係賣嚟食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T04:16:32.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n運嘅過程可能已經冇命"},{"pid":"bc3d94f97e46563ab57161d76e131c4300b5f0f1","tid":2492293,"uid":85427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T04:17:09.000